In a message dated 1/7/03 6:07:18 PM Central Standard Time,
Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com writes:

<< Is Zeum a unique place or does it have other branches? >>

It sounds like a lot of the other science/hands on museums around the
country. You can usually buy a membership to one and get into LOADS of them.
We did some animation at the Birmingham science museum, it was SO cool. I was
really wishing we had equipment after that!

Ren
